#compdef pytr
# Documentation: https://github.com/pytr-org/pytr/blob/master/README.md
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-20
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above. Removed from prior file:
# `accounts` and `cancel_order` subcommands - neither exist in README.

# pytr: Trade Republic CLI
_arguments -s -S \
  '(-h --help)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(-V --version)'{-V,--version}'[show version]' \
  '-v[verbosity level]:level:(warning info debug)' \
  '--debug-logfile=[dump debug logs to file]:file:_files' \
  '--debug-log-filter=[filter debug log types]:filter:' \
  '1:command:(help login portfolio details dl_docs export_transactions get_price_alarms set_price_alarms get_savings_plans completion)' \
  '*::arguments:_default'
